column2: select s.specObjId, s.bestObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z_person, s.class_person, s.comments_person, s.class, s.subClass, p.nChild, p.type, p.flags, p.ra, p.dec, p.raErr, p.decErr, p.b, p.l, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, e.ra, e.dec, e.z, e.zerr, e.bpt, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#, e.Flux_Cont_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, e.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#, e.Flux_Cont_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, e.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err, w.cntr, w.ra, w.dec, w.sigra, w.sigdec, w.sigradec, w.w1mpro, w.w1sigmpro, w.w1snr, w.w2mpro, w.w2sigmpro, w.w2snr, w.w3mpro, w.w3sigmpro, w.w3snr, w.w4mpro, w.w4sigmpro, w.w4snr from wise_xmatch as xm  join SpecObjAll as s on xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID  join PhotoObjAll as p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objID  join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID  join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr  join galSpecLine as g on s.specObjID = g.specObjID where xm.match_dist<=# and s.zwarning=# and e.z># and e.zerr/e.z<=# and e.z<=# and w.w1cc_map=# and w.w2cc_map=# and w.w3cc_map=# and w.w4cc_map=# and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and s.class=&&& and s.subClass=&&& and (w.w1mpro-w.w2mpro)>=# and (e.Flux_OIII_#=# or e.Flux_OIII_#<=e.Flux_OIII_#_Err)
